description:
This tanned guy is Mike Matters. Coming from Canada, this bilingual hunk is here to show off his stuff.

When he's not stripping, he's either working out, or working in his shop, building race cars. For this scene, Mike will be showing you that a wrench isn't the only tool he knows how to handle; he's quite good handling his 7” uncut tool too!

Enjoy!
title: Mike Matters
